headline: Colgate-Palmolive Co (CL) Q2 2025 Earnings Call Highlights: Resilient Growth Amidst Challenges
summary: Colgate-Palmolive Co (CL) reports strong sales and earnings growth, strategic acquisitions, and innovative launches despite facing raw material pressures and a cautious consumer environment.
